## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6efc8-143">このプロパティの既定値は `System.String.Empty` です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6efc8-143">The default value of this property is `System.String.Empty`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6efc8-144">アプリケーションは、の<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>値を完全に変更することができます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6efc8-144">Applications are free to completely change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6efc8-145">の<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>値をリセットしても、と<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>の<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A>値は変更されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6efc8-145">Resetting the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A> will not change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextOffset%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextLength%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
